00:21:18.140 --> 00:21:20.304
Student:  Well,
I guess the predominant

00:21:20.304 --> 00:21:23.286
economic philosophy at the time
when Adam Smith was writing was

00:21:23.286 --> 00:21:25.650
mercantilism--
Prof: Mercantilism, yes.

00:21:25.650 --> 00:21:27.818
Student: 
&gt;

00:21:27.818 --> 00:21:28.748
mercantilism,
which is, you know,

00:21:28.748 --> 00:21:29.848
accumulate as much gold as
possible;

00:21:29.848 --> 00:21:31.963
become the richest,
