00:23:35.740 --> 00:23:42.439
So that Smith talks about the
self-interest axiom as the

00:23:42.439 --> 00:23:47.190
driver for promoting the common
good.

00:23:47.190 --> 00:23:52.538
Now I'm going to invite Jim
